    "Crea alarmas para cumpleaños, aniversarios y eventos personales. Suenan aunque tu iPhone esté en silencio.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Create alarms for birthdays, anniversaries, and personal events. They ring even when your iPhone is silent."
